  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: b6198cdbfb3ab42799698812d172dc50, type: 3}
  m_Name: Mara
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ISUGameDev.SpearGame.Dialogue.Dialogue
  dialogueStrings:
  - The trickster has run away.
  - Worry not, Valkyrie, I will bring Loki many nightmares in his defeat.
  - That is, if you manage to vanquish him.
  - You need not do so in my name.
  - Then I will do so in mine. I will have much satisfaction in doing so.
  - "Very well\u2026I suppose\u2026 "
  - "Seeing as you\u2019re here, what do you know of Ragnarok? Where is Loki?"
  - "Ah\u2026he is likely in the realm of Jotunheim."
  - It is where Ymir was slain and dissolved into a lake of his own blood.
  - If Loki has discovered how to bring Surtr to the 9 realms, Jotunheim would be
    the place to summon him.
  - I suppose I know my next destination then.
  - "Hm\u2026Valkyrie\u2026?"
  - "\u2026?"
  - I give you my luck.
  - "I would very much enjoy Loki\u2019s prodding mind."
  - "Thanks\u2026"
  - Farewell.
  characterIcon: {fileID: 0}
  characterName: Mara
